name: Life is a rollercoaster
description:
I should know by now we shouldn't make plans,
we are metal drops moving through a field of magnets.
I should know by now that life is a roller coaster,
you go from wanting to be dead to almost die laughing.

1200x1200px GIF
Frame-by-frame animation of the cover art for my song "Montaña Rusa" (Roller Coaster). For private non commercial use only. To view more of my work, have a chat or listen to my music, find me on IG as @tatoquesada
